<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.5.1">
<l>vantuṉa taṭiyēṉ maṉampukun tāypukun tataṟpiṉ ṇaṅkumeṉ</l>
<l>cinta ṉaikkiṉi yāytiru vēyeṉ ṉāruyirē</l>
<l>antaḷi raṇiyā racōki ṉiḷantaḷir kaḷkalan tavaiyeṅkum</l>
<l>centaḻal puraiyum tiruvā liyammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having come [here], you entered the mind of your servant, me;</l>
<l rend="indent">after entering, you are sweetness for my thoughts which revere [you],</l>
<l>My treasure, my dear life,</l>
<l>Lord of sacred Āli where young leaves of the aśoka [tree],</l>
<l rend="indent">covered with beautiful bud ornaments,</l>
<l>Being jumbled everywhere, resemble scarlet flames.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
